 y begins\n​Prize Money: ​1st place: $1\,000 ​2nd place: $750\nR1 wil
 l be provided (teams will provide remaining positions) USAV Rules and Unif
 orm Requirements will be followed.\n\nDEADLINE TO ENTER - MAY 13TH AT 3PM:
 \nTeams are not required to be registered for USAV Open Adult National Cha
 mpionships\nIf you have any questions about this event\, please reach out 
 to [email protected] or give our office a call at (352) 742-0080\n15010 U
 S Highway 441 Eustis\, Fl 32726\n[email protected]\n(352) 742-0080\n\nHEL
 PFUL LINKS:\n- Membership Information\n- Indoor Jr. Bids and Rankings\n- 
 ​Sanction a USAV Event\n- Find a Club\n- Events and Event Schedule\n- Be
 come an Official\n- Request COI\n- Policies & Procedures\n\nOFFICE HOURS:\
