 pendence Day\, Labor Day\, Thanksgiving Day\, Thanksgiving Friday\, Christ
 mas Eve through New Years Day\nCopyright (c) 1982-2025 Florida Region of U
 SA Volleyball\, Inc. All Rights Reserved. Designed by StellarBlue.ai\n\nMo
 re info: https://floridavolleyball.org/blog/event/2026-florida-adult-regio
 nal-championships/
